<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf0537267-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9094"><num value="9094">§ 9094.</num><heading> Assignment of payments</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idf0537268-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9094/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s590h/g">section 590h(g) of title 16</ref>, relating to assignment of payments, shall apply to payments made under this chapter.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idf0537269-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s9094/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Notice</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The producer making the assignment, or the assignee, shall provide the Secretary with notice, in such manner as the Secretary may require, of any assignment made under this section.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idf053726a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/79/tI/s1611">Pub. L. 113–79, title I, § 1611</ref>, <date date="2014-02-07">Feb. 7, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/710">128 Stat. 710</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idf053726b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idf053726c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idf053726d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This chapter, referred to in subsec. (a), was in the original “this title”, meaning title I of <ref href="/us/pl/113/79">Pub. L. 113–79</ref>, <date date="2014-02-07">Feb. 7, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/649">128 Stat. 649</ref>, which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of title I to the Code, see Tables.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
